===Noun===
'''[[drag]] [[queen]]'''
#{{slang}} A man who dresses up as a woman for performance purposes. A drag queen is not necessarily [[homosexual]], and being a drag queen is not a reliable indicator of sexual orientation. The term "drag queen" refers to a profession, in the same way that doctor, plumber or teacher do. This differs to the term "[[transvestite]]", which refers to a character trait, in the same way that thespian, thrillseeker and liar do.

